column5: Hey,  I'm looking to pop my boat in somewhere around Bradford into simcoe......Does anybody know of any launches nearby? Possibly thinking I may like to fish the mouth of the holland marsh river..possibly killarney bay?? I live in toronto, so ideally, any launch in simcoe which would be closest to toronto would be the greatest....I'm heading out with a few ppl who would be looking for the least amount of commuting...    Any suggestions would be great  thank you!  -Mark
You can launch right at the Holland River, off highway 11.  Joey
